B.a0S=new A.I("Aviation Collocation Patterns","Aviation English uses specific word combinations that don't follow general English rules. Study collocations from ICAO training materials systematically.")
B.a0k=new A.I("Safety Announcement Templates","Standard safety announcements follow fixed templates. Master the exact phrasing for each type of announcement \u2014 these appear frequently in fill-blank exams.")
